# Privacy Policy for Nepal Driving Licence तयारी

"Nepal Driving Licence तयारी" is an offline quiz app developed to assist users in preparing for driving license exams. We understand the importance of privacy, and this Privacy Policy outlines the types of information the app collects and how it is used.

## Information Collection and Usage

### No Personal Data Collection

"Nepal Driving Licence तयारी" does not collect or store any personal information from its users. We do not require users to create accounts or provide personal details to use the app.

### Quiz Data

The app may collect data related to quiz performance, such as quiz scores, answers, and progress. This data is used solely for the purpose of enhancing the user experience and improving the app's functionality. It is stored locally on the user's device and is not transmitted or shared with any external parties.

## Data Security

We take the security of user data seriously. All data collected by the app is stored locally on the user's device and is not accessible to anyone else. We implement security measures to protect data from unauthorized access or disclosure.

## Third-Party Services

The app may use third-party services for analytical purposes or to display advertisements. These services may have their own privacy policies and terms of service. Users are encouraged to review the privacy policies of these third-party services for a better understanding of their data collection practices.

## Children's Privacy

"Nepal Driving Licence तयारी" is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that their child has provided us with personal information without their consent, they should contact us, and we will promptly delete the information.

## Changes to Privacy Policy

Any updates or changes to this Privacy Policy will be reflected within the app. Users are encouraged to review the Privacy Policy periodically for any modifications.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at [contact@drivinglicenceapp.com](mailto:contact@drivinglicenceapp.com).

By using "Nepal Driving Licence तयारी," you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this Privacy Policy.
